he subject area of the email can also be auto loaded.</p>\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> When adding the subject, rather than using spaces between words it is important to write <code>%20</code> in place of each space.</p>\n<p>Example:</p>\n<pre><code class="language-html">&#x3C;a\n  href="mailto:heya@enki.com?\n        subject=Sign%20me%20up!">\nEmail me to sign up.\n&#x3C;/a>\n</code></pre>\n<!--[View CodePen](https://codepen.io/enkidevs/pen/OwpKGj)-->\n',
